      "content": "thanks. i tried some water but i still feel kinda weird like my brain is foggy and i'm stumbling a bit. u think i should just keep resting and maybe grab some electrolyte drinks from the corner store? i dont really want to go to a hospital if i can help it, it seems like overkill for just being in the sun too long.",
