      "content": "okay but an hour or two is a long time to wait if it's bad. i'm just really worried about the cost of the hospital here and honestly it just feels like i'm overheated. if i just take some aspirin and drink a ton of Gatorade and stay in the ac, that should fix it right? i really just want to sleep it off.",
